<D>__{it's good to be home, sir.}
<A>__{mandela just nods. too tired to talk. hendrick escorts mandela to the mercedes, opens the door for him. mandela takes a step towards the open door and staggers. reflexively, hendrick reaches out, steadies him.}
<C>__{mandela}
<D>__{i'm fine.}
<A>__{mandela steps out of hendrick's hands, holds onto the open door.}
<C>__{mandela}
<D>__{travelling the world, begging for money, is very tiring.}
<A>__{mandela reaches into his jacket, pulls a small package out, hands it to hendrick.}
<C>__{mandela}
<D>__{this is for you.}
